README
===

Training: using `ex2.py --train=sample-training-data.txt --model=modelfile --ngram-length=2`

Testing: using `ex2.py --test=sample-test-data.txt --model=modelfile --smooth=0.1`


Now for convience, I fixed the parameter in the main() function, if you want to execute using other paramters, just modify the assigning of parameter in the function, I think it's not convienent for debugging when inputting so many parameters in the commander line, so just execute by `./ex2.py` is OK now.
